snippet.title: Joel Nielsen - Devolve Online Soundtrack - Entropy
snippet.description:
The in-game music for Devolve Online—an open-world action MMORPG created by me, my wife, and some friends! Check it out now at https://www.devolveonline.com.

This video was captured entirely in-game in a single continuous take.

The music is also available on itunes, spotify, amazon, etc...
